snippet.title: Camila Cabello Reveals The Untold Truth Of Her Breakup with Shawn Mendes
snippet.description:
Camila Cabello Reveals The Untold Truth Of Her Breakup with Shawn Mendes 
Camilla Cabello is giving all the tea about her split from Shawn and you just might be surprised why they actually broke up. Speaking on the split, Camilla revealed that she has for a long time, struggled with anxiety that became so “crippling,” eventually affecting her relationship. The singer attributed her anxiety to feeling burned out after years and years of endless hard work in the entertainment industry.
